Invocation Name: bruce lee facts
des:
*UNOFFICIAL Bruce Lee Facts skill*

Learn random and essential facts about Bruce Lee, one of the most iconic martial artists of all-time!


Example conversation: 

USER: "Alexa, tell me a Bruce Lee fact."

ALEXA: "Bruce Lee was born on November 27, 1940, in Chinatown, San Francisco, California."



Prerequisite: Any Alexa-enabled device.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
